Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.81,0:00:11.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Fight 不要回頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.73,0:00:14.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Fight 邁步出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.90,0:00:17.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,眼淚是閃閃發光的勇氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.90,0:00:20.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,每一步 都化為甘霖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.88,0:00:25.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Fight Fight 更加自信了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.41,0:00:36.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不需要的東西就捨去 這樣也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.50,0:00:42.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在無限廣闊的心中蔓延開來喲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.78,0:00:48.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,於受傷時刻之外　看不見的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.83,0:00:54.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,若現在開始映入雙眸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.78,0:00:56.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Just Try-again
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.11,0:01:01.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,變得強大 抓住機會啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.10,0:01:07.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Fight 無論何時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.11,0:01:10.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Fight 都要堅信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.14,0:01:13.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,夢想絕對能實現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.23,0:01:16.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有多遙遠 都不害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.23,0:01:22.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Fight Fight 更能感覺到明天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.09,0:01:33.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我叫戰部渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.60,0:01:37.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為了打倒支配了在遙遠天空上的星界山的多壞達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.50,0:01:41.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們以第七星界 為目標展開了冒險旅程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.13,0:01:43.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,進入了聖天界的我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.01,0:01:47.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要在這裏各自尋找自己的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.56,0:01:50.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,回到了出身地麾利多村的海火子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.23,0:01:53.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在那裏遇上了在自己出世前的父親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.37,0:01:55.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,漂亮的把愛得到手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.14,0:01:59.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今天也會是"超"有趣又有型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.02,0:02:08.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第三十四話\N古拿瑪!再一次的愛!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.19,0:02:18.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,成功了…找到愛了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.81,0:02:21.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,火美子第一,火子第二!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.79,0:02:24.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,成功了…找到愛了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.37,0:02:28.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,火美子和海火子也找到愛回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.08,0:02:30.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好了,下一個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.68,0:02:35.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,古拿瑪,是你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.29,0:02:40.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去找回來,在那一天你失去了的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.75,0:02:41.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.73,0:02:46.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼了?古拿瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.43,0:02:49.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,古拿瑪,失去了的意思到底是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.63,0:02:52.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那種東西…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.87,0:02:54.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果你說不想去的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.24,0:02:57.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,便等於放棄松明瞭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.07,0:03:00.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,古拿瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.49,0:03:03.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鳥先生也快點去找到愛,拿這個回來啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.75,0:03:07.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,古拿瑪…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.15,0:03:11.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明白了,我去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.45,0:03:14.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鳥先生,慢慢行了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.19,0:03:18.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,古拿瑪…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.87,0:03:32.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這…這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.48,0:03:43.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,果然是這裏嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.88,0:04:19.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等等!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.06,0:04:30.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你稍微太過囂張了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.34,0:04:47.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們的地頭我們終有一天會收下的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.37,0:05:08.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,由莉亞…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.90,0:05:11.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嘻,被打一身了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.14,0:05:17.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,古拿瑪真蠢材
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.56,0:05:37.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,由莉亞,你看著了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.40,0:05:44.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.11,0:05:47.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要這樹一日仍存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.64,0:05:49.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們的名字也會留下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.91,0:05:51.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,由莉亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.15,0:05:53.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,古拿瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.52,0:05:57.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,古拿瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.73,0:05:59.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你又打架了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.46,0:06:03.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我只是還禮給他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.62,0:06:05.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,求求你,請你不要再打了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.06,0:06:07.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這可不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.50,0:06:10.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,當著同伴的面,不好好做過了斷不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.13,0:06:16.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣繼續爭鬥下去會有什麼結果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.47,0:06:19.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.22,0:06:20.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,求求你,不要再打了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.02,0:06:22.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,由莉亞…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.49,0:06:34.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,古拿瑪!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.52,0:06:38.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,找你很久了,古拿瑪!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.99,0:06:39.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.93,0:06:41.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對方的首領提出了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.59,0:06:43.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一對一的決鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.86,0:06:45.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要好好做一個了斷呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.13,0:06:47.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.32,0:06:48.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這是好機會啊,古拿瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.20,0:06:50.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這次打倒他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.91,0:06:52.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,便可以保護我們的領土了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.74,0:06:56.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不快點的話便沒時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.37,0:06:57.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拜託你,古拿瑪!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.88,0:06:59.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,古拿瑪求求你,不要去!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.51,0:07:02.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,古拿瑪,你這樣也算是男人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.02,0:07:05.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別人挑起的架,必打是我們的規條啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.39,0:07:10.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要打架了,古拿瑪!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.55,0:07:11.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,古拿瑪!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.10,0:07:16.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.23,0:07:18.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,古拿瑪!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.00,0:07:20.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這是女人不會明白的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.67,0:07:53.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣便分出勝負了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.53,0:07:54.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,死心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.25,0:07:56.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,停手!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.45,0:07:58.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,由莉亞…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.84,0:08:01.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這不是只會令爭鬥繼續下去嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.64,0:08:02.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要再打了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.48,0:08:06.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,求求你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.70,0:08:07.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.08,0:08:09.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.79,0:08:13.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不想失去你!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.99,0:08:22.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可惡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.40,0:08:27.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,古拿瑪!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.08,0:08:43.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,由莉亞!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.74,0:08:47.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,由莉亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.58,0:08:48.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,振作點,由莉亞!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.21,0:08:51.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,古拿瑪…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.62,0:08:52.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蠢材!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.97,0:08:54.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你為什麼要來?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.63,0:08:58.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我…對你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.97,0:09:03.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,由莉亞…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.84,0:09:05.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,由莉亞!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.01,0:09:17.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去尋找愛嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.70,0:09:35.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,難…難道…由莉亞?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.81,0:09:42.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不可以去的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.45,0:09:52.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.93,0:09:54.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.55,0:09:57.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對救命恩人不是這樣的口吻吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.09,0:10:00.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,由莉亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.14,0:10:02.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.80,0:10:05.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,總而言之,突然推倒人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.28,0:10:07.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還說是救命恩人是什麼意思?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.37,0:10:10.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你真的不知道嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.07,0:10:12.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.09,0:10:13.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,剛才的是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.30,0:10:16.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,人說的看見了便是死期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.34,0:10:19.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,永遠令人長眠的睡眠雷姆啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.95,0:10:20.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,雷姆?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.55,0:10:22.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.76,0:10:23.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.46,0:10:25.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,知道了要感謝我了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.05,0:10:28.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,雖然我不喜歡被強迫的謝人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.05,0:10:30.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,姑且謝謝你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.67,0:10:32.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.06,0:10:35.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不可以再誠摯一點說多謝的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.20,0:10:36.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,總而言之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.39,0:10:40.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要因為是美麗的女人便流口水呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.13,0:10:41.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.51,0:10:45.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你可不要亂說啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.59,0:10:56.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是破爛的旅店呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.98,0:11:00.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,歡迎光臨,要住宿嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.39,0:11:01.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.45,0:11:03.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,暫時睡一晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.46,0:11:05.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,給我最便宜的房間便可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.53,0:11:07.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這裏哪間房都很便宜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.61,0:11:08.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為是破旅店吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.13,0:11:11.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大哥哥,你由哪裏來的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.20,0:11:14.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,古莉亞,你對客人胡說什麼啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.37,0:11:18.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對不起,我女兒說了失禮的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.47,0:11:19.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不,不要緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.44,0:11:21.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,姐姐!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.34,0:11:23.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,歡迎回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.98,0:11:27.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.25,0:11:33.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼?你是我們的客人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.72,0:11:35.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你認識我的女兒的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.49,0:11:38.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊…是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.31,0:11:40.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣的話你早點說啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.91,0:11:42.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.64,0:11:43.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,歡迎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.48,0:11:45.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,呀…你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.21,0:12:03.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,叫我去尋找愛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.82,0:12:07.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,星星這麼罕見嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.39,0:12:10.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜莉亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.35,0:12:13.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你已一直站在這裏幾小時了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.74,0:12:15.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是我的自由吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.90,0:12:21.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你剛才把雷姆認錯是另一個人了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.83,0:12:22.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.74,0:12:25.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你曾把我叫過由莉亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.85,0:12:27.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是那個人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.07,0:12:30.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果是又怎樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.35,0:12:32.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也不是有什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.45,0:12:34.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但看你好像很哀傷的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.15,0:12:37.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你可不可以不要理別人的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.58,0:12:38.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.87,0:12:39.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.12,0:12:41.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,請別介意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.43,0:12:53.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,餵,你打算住多久…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.41,0:12:57.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.39,0:12:58.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真討厭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.00,0:13:00.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,古怪的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.02,0:13:03.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,冷的話便用那個爐吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.49,0:13:04.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.76,0:13:23.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,由莉亞…把由莉亞還給我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.64,0:13:27.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果你愛由莉亞的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.01,0:13:29.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我便還給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.80,0:13:30.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.24,0:13:33.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你愛由莉亞嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.11,0:13:35.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,當然愛了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.62,0:13:38.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼,為什麼不聽由莉亞的請求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.06,0:13:41.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也因為這樣由莉亞才會死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.58,0:13:43.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這…這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.81,0:13:46.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你並沒有愛由莉亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.15,0:13:48.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.79,0:13:52.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,由莉亞是被你那虛假的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.44,0:13:54.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,欺騙痛苦地死去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.66,0:13:56.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你沒有愛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.93,0:13:57.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.94,0:13:59.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是真的愛她的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.18,0:14:01.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.94,0:14:05.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,由莉亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.88,0:14:07.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,由莉亞!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.84,0:14:12.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,由莉亞…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.08,0:14:18.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,姐姐!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.02,0:14:27.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,姐姐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.35,0:14:28.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,餵,起來啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.74,0:14:29.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,姐姐!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.50,0:14:32.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.07,0:14:37.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,姐姐…姐姐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.67,0:14:39.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這到底是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.87,0:14:42.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她看見雷姆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.44,0:14:44.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼?雷姆出現了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.31,0:14:50.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒有救她的方法嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.82,0:14:52.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只有一個方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.28,0:14:57.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果得到在鎮外沼澤沙洲中盛開的花的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.82,0:14:59.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是沒可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.42,0:15:02.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒有真實的愛的人進入那沼澤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.62,0:15:04.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是不會有命回來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.30,0:15:07.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真實的愛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.30,0:15:10.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你沒有愛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.20,0:15:15.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,姐姐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.62,0:15:31.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個沼澤在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.07,0:15:49.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是那裏嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.38,0:16:00.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到現在為止架橋過去的、用船過去的人也有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.39,0:16:01.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是也不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.97,0:16:05.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那沼澤是人類自己走進去的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.42,0:16:07.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是過不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.20,0:16:21.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒有真實的愛的人進入那沼澤是不會有命回來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.68,0:16:27.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,由莉亞…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.89,0:16:37.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,古拿瑪,不要去!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.09,0:16:39.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,由…由莉亞!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.99,0:16:41.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,古拿瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.17,0:16:42.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要再幹危險的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.26,0:16:46.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果你愛我的話,便不要去!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.17,0:16:48.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,由莉亞!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.34,0:16:53.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,古拿瑪,你是愛我的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.29,0:16:55.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那你便把那證據給我看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.60,0:16:57.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,過來這裏,古拿瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.89,0:17:00.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,由莉亞…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.99,0:17:08.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,古拿瑪!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.15,0:17:11.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不可以啊,古拿瑪,不要去!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.66,0:17:12.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,古拿瑪 求求你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.04,0:17:15.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是愛我的話,便不要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.55,0:17:17.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還是說你不愛我嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.70,0:17:21.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你還記得嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.42,0:17:24.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在和你相識之前的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.46,0:17:25.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不知道什麼是愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.01,0:17:28.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不,連知也不想知
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.98,0:17:32.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那時候的我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.63,0:17:34.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只會想我自己的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.18,0:17:39.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,每天胡亂傷害身邊的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.12,0:17:40.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.09,0:17:48.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,"這樣的生活並不是人生"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.76,0:17:51.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,由莉亞…是你告訴我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.23,0:17:55.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.82,0:17:57.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,認識了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.26,0:17:58.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的人生改變了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.54,0:18:01.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想和你一起生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.23,0:18:04.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想永遠保護你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.48,0:18:08.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要說,不要說!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.58,0:18:12.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我打算那次是最後的,在那次決鬥之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.72,0:18:14.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我打算和我的同伴告別的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.49,0:18:17.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這個只是狡辯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.58,0:18:18.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是狡辯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.79,0:18:19.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,騙人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.81,0:18:22.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你並沒有愛由莉亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.53,0:18:27.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是深深愛過你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.69,0:18:29.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不,現在仍然愛你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.02,0:18:42.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,由莉亞!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.23,0:18:59.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.43,0:19:06.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,由莉亞…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.58,0:19:17.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,請幫我,由莉亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.24,0:19:46.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,由莉亞…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.21,0:20:14.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜莉亞!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.81,0:20:15.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,姐姐!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.96,0:20:17.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爸爸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.29,0:20:18.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.31,0:20:21.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是古拿瑪先生替你取沼澤的花來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.98,0:20:23.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,古拿瑪?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.31,0:20:24.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竟為了我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.12,0:20:28.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,古拿瑪呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.52,0:20:31.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.29,0:20:33.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,古拿瑪先生他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.19,0:20:37.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是嗎,他走了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.01,0:20:41.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個人擁有真實的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.05,0:20:45.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他是真的愛由莉亞小姐呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.95,0:21:33.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,古拿瑪!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.92,0:21:34.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎樣了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.56,0:21:39.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,找到愛了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.06,0:21:41.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,做得好,古拿瑪!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.06,0:21:43.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是,古拿瑪…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.53,0:21:45.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你好像不太高興呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.43,0:21:47.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒有這回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.07,0:21:48.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,古拿瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.60,0:21:53.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看來你找到失去的東西了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.21,0:21:55.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼,下一個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.28,0:21:57.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,武一郎,到你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.18,0:21:59.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.00,0:22:01.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,師父,沒問題嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.58,0:22:02.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,交給我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.83,0:22:04.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我用這劍起誓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.25,0:22:05.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我會把愛找出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.42,0:22:36.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現在 陰霾的天空裏烏雲漸漸散去 陽光透過雲層照了下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.99,0:22:46.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,兩個人仰望這天空的哪個角落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.11,0:22:52.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,眩目的彩虹 即將出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.84,0:22:54.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,注定出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.66,0:22:57.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快走吧 奔跑吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.29,0:23:01.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,趁著光線還沒有消失的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.72,0:23:08.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,期待著明天的幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.87,0:23:12.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快走吧 奔跑吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.45,0:23:15.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,熠熠生輝的彩虹彼岸裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.86,0:23:24.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,吹出了兩個人未來的風
